ing: 1/3 cup seeded and chopped jalapeno pepper
des: "A hint of spice makes this creamy dip great with chips, crackers, or fresh veggies. Can also be used as a dressing on a salad or tossed with pasta."
ins: Blend buttermilk, green chilies, mayonnaise, jalapeno pepper, cilantro, garlic, ranch dressing mix, and lime juice in a food processor or blender until mostly smooth.
